     <h2>
      <a href="/">
       mnmlst
      </a>
      :
      <b>
       tng lss t b lghtr
      </b>
     </h2>
     <div class="entry">
      <p>
       Whl y mght rd  lt f psts bt th mnmlst sthtc, s wll s n wnng lss stff, wht sn’t tlkd bt ngh s mnmlst tng.
      </p>
      <p>
       As Amrcns, w t wy t mch (nd wst t mch fd s wll). As smn wh ws t lst 60 lbs. vrwght nly  fw yrs g, I pckd wy th fd s mch s nyn ls. I knw wht t’s lk t t ntr pzzs by myslf, t spr-szd fst-fd mls pls xtr nggts nd dssrts nd mr, fnsh th ggntc hpng plts f fd tht th rstrnts srv ths dys.
      </p>
      <p>
       It’s t mch, nd t’s ld t n bsty pdmc f lrmng prprtns. A lrg prt f r hlthcr crss s bcs f r vrtng.
      </p>
      <p>
       A gd prt f th sltn s t smply t lss.
      </p>
      <p>
       A sprt dscssn shld b bt wht w t — rgnc, rl fds, prfrbly grwn lclly, ckd t hm wth  mnmm f prcssng nd pckgng. Bt tdy, I’d jst lk t tlk bt tng lss.
      </p>
      <p>
       It’s smthng I’v fcsd n n my wn lf, spclly rcntly, s I lk t nt nly qlty f fd bt qntty. I thnk w’v bn cndtnd t t wtht thnkng, nd n dng s t t wy t mch. T stff rslvs ntl w’r grgd. Whch f crs sn’t hlthy t ll.
      </p>
      <p>
       My fcs hs bn n tng ntl I’m nt qt fll. I t ntl I fl lk I wnt  lttl mr, nd thn ps. Brth. In bt 10 mnts, I rlz I’m stsfd nd dn’t nd t t ny mr.
      </p>
      <p>
       Sm tps f y’d lk t ccmplsh ths:
      </p>
      <ul>
       <li>
        Only tk  smll prtn t strt wth. Dn’t hp th plt.
       </li>
       <li>
        Et slwly nd mndflly.
       </li>
       <li>
        Ps btwn bts. Svr th fd.
       </li>
       <li>
        Stp bfr y’r fll, nd wt.
       </li>
       <li>
        Drnk wtr wth yr fd.
       </li>
       <li>
        Et vry 2-3 hrs, r mbrc th hngr nd wt  lttl lngr.
       </li>
       <li>
        If y gt hngry gn sn ftr, t  smll snck —  frt, sm vggs,  hndfl f nts.
       </li>
       <li>
        Ct bck slwly. Dn’t try t t lk  brd t frst. Jst t  lttl lss fr nw, djst, nd thn ct bck  lttl mr.
       </li>
      </ul>
      <p>
       Ovr tm, y’ll chng, nd b bl t t lss. Y’ll b hlthr (ssmng y wr tng t mch bfr) nd lghtr nd lvng mr sstnbly.
      </p>
